TED Talk on Wellness.

@lizwell11 If you want to be healthier but don’t know where to start, start simple. The small habits that seem mundane or boring are often overlooked because a lot of us want a quick fix. Yet our health and wellness journey is just that, a journey. Long term sustainable habits are what will make a difference not crash diets, ‘health foods’ or magic supplements.
